  "prompt": "How long does it typically take to receive quotations as a buyer from ThunderQuote?",
  "response": "The time it typically takes to receive quotations as a buyer from ThunderQuote can vary depending on several factors, including the complexity of your request, the number of suppliers available, and their responsiveness. Generally, you can expect to receive quotations within a few hours to a couple of business days after submitting your request. However, for more specialized or complex projects, it may take a bit longer for suppliers to provide detailed quotes.\n\nTo expedite the process, ensure that your request is clear, detailed, and includes all necessary specifications. ThunderQuote\u2019s platform is designed to streamline the process, connecting you with relevant suppliers quickly. If you need urgent quotes, you may also reach out directly to ThunderQuote\u2019s support team for assistance.",
